event.title: I ♥ Free Software Day in Arnhem, Netherlands

body.p: Strategically placed at the centre of the country, the meeting in Arnhem can accommodate people from all Netherlands. The teem meets for a cosy dinner and a drink. Please announce your attendance in the Dutch mailing list. We are meeting at📍 Momento Oude Oeverstraat 98 6811 JZ , at ⏰ 19:00.
